{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"eff8728efd","title":"给吴启瑞的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2cd9e23e4b","index":0,"year":1950,"month":7,"day":19,"articleId":"eff8728efd"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"8ab960980d","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"eff8728efd","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"吴启瑞是毛泽东在湖南省立第一师范学校读书时的数学教师王立庵的儿娘。当时在无锡师范学校附属小学做教员。"}],"contents":[{"id":"68d54e3c2b","type":"title","text":"给吴启瑞“的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"eff8728efd"},{"id":"8ab960980d","type":"paragraph","text":"启瑞先生：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"eff8728efd"},{"id":"f5947174fa","type":"paragraph","text":"五月来信收到，困难情形，甚为系念。所请准予你的三个小孩加入苏南干部子弟班，减轻你的困难一事，请持此信与当地适当机关的负责同志商量一下，看是否可行。找什么人商量由你的定，如有必要可去找苏南区党委书记陈不显同志一商。我是没有不赞成的，就是不知道该子弟班有容纳较多的小孩之可能否？你是八个孩子的母亲，望加保重，并为我问候你的孩子们。此复，并颂教祺！","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"eff8728efd"},{"id":"ffc23de778","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"eff8728efd"},{"id":"9731f1430b","type":"paragraph","text":"七月十九日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"eff8728efd"}],"page":{"id":"04dc6e59fd","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"eff8728efd","start":38,"end":38}}}},"__N_SSG":true}